            (weight: 2, text: "The silence that followed said more than words ever could."),
            (weight: 2, text: "{subject} exhaled slowly, as if releasing years of burden. {body_language}"),
            (weight: 2, text: "And just like that, the careful architecture of their evening crumbled."),
